These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, reading, skydiving, writing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, drama, martial-arts, satire
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, orchid, daisy, iris
1. the person who growstulip is the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is writing is in an odd position##4
4. the person who growsorchid is on the left or right of the person who growsiris##3
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
6. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
7. the person who growsorchid is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who growsiris is between the person watching satire movies and the person who's hobby is hiking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Hobby         | writing      | hiking | reading | skydiving |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | crime  | drama   | satire    |
| Flower     | tulip     | daisy    | iris    | orchid      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, singing, sudoku, video-games
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, plum, artichoke, cherry
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, boat, jet-ski, taxi
1. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person eating artichoke##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an even position##4
4. the person driving the airplane is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person eating plum##1
7. the person eating grapefruit is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's hobby is singing##2
8. the person eating cherry is between the person eating plum and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | video-games | sudoku   | singing | dancing  |
| Food   | artichoke     | grapefruit | cherry  | plum |
| Transport     | taxi        | jet-ski  | boat    | airplane |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, kiwi, lemon, tomato
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, volleyball, swimming, skiing
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, roller, snowmobile, train
1. the person who's sport is skiing is between the person eating grapefruit and the person eating tomato##2
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person driving the train##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is the person eating lemon##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
5. the person eating tomato is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is swimming is between the person eating kiwi and the person who's sport is sailing##2
7. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | grapefruit | kiwi   | tomato     | lemon     |
| Sport   | volleyball  | skiing | swimming   | sailing  |
| Transport     | train      | roller | snowmobile | motorbike |

