.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, collecting, drawing, singing
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, march, february, november
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, disco, electronic, house
1. the fan of house is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
2. the person who's birthday is in february is the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the person who's birthday is in november is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
5. the fan of disco is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who's hobby is chess##2
6. the fan of house is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
7. the person who's hobby is chess is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person who's hobby is drawing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | collecting | chess      | drawing       | singing    |
| Birthday           | march  | february  | november | august |
| Music-Genre   | house      | electronic | disco         | country    |

