4. the fan of gospel is on the far left or far right##3
5. the colombian is on the left of the german##1
6. the fan of gospel is in an odd position##4
7. the nigerian is on the far left or far right##3
8. the fan of jazz is the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Music-Genre          | gospel | jazz  | trance   | funk    |
